---
title: Slow-Cooked Chicken & Creamy Risoni Bake with Baby Broccoli & Parmesan Cheese
description: Patience is going to be key with this dish. We understand how tempting it is to dig in as soon as possible - it smells so good - but you’ll be
glad for those extra minutes. Allowing the succulent chicken to marinate in the creamy stew will add a burst of flavour to every bite.

